com.ibm.di.connector.dpa.schema

Class ReferenceInstance

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibm.di.connector.dpa.schema.ReferenceInstance

  • public class ReferenceInstance
extends java.lang.Object
    The instances of this class contain one or more ClassInstance objects referred by another ClassInstance object. Each reference instance object has a corresponding ReferenceDefinition.
